The '''black-fronted flowerpecker''' ('''''Dicaeum igniferum''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Dicaeidae]]. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to the [[Lesser Sunda Islands]] in [[Indonesia]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]].

